&lt;p&gt;Own full-cycle recruitment for field leadership roles (Head Coach, Assistant Coach, Area Leader) across assigned regions, managing a portfolio of ~30+ active openings at a time&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Partner closely with Regional General Managers, Area Leaders, and People Business Partners to identify talent needs, align on candidate profiles, and move with urgency on P0/P1 priorities&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lead confidential and executive-level searches with discretion, creativity, and professionalism&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Manage sourcing strategy across tools, including Greenhouse, LinkedIn, Indeed, Fountain, Recruitics, and BrightHire&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Maintain data integrity in ChartHop and Greenhouse; ensure accurate pipeline tracking and timely role management&lt;/p&gt;
