&lt;p&gt;Manage cost structures, aligning cost of goods sold with company financial targets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Achieve cost savings targets through strategic initiatives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Enhance operator service metrics, including on-time delivery, order accuracy, and full specifications compliance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
